title: Ahimsa Vegetarian Restaurant
description: Food is simple, space is clean. No fridge, but ice in drinks is made from mineral water. Directions: Go just south of the Central Station along main road Jalan Kebon Jati heading west, it is the small alley on the left when coming from Kebon Jati going west.
streetAddress: Jl. Kebonjati Blk 41 Komp. Luxor Permai Kav. 25, Bandung, West Java
